{"tid":843164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 獨居翁單位傳出惡臭　揭死去數星期變腐屍","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T07:08:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8f88ba1a123d738aba75215940ce2fc685a9a22d","tid":843164,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"今日(1日)凌晨零時36分，油麻地炮台街14號德利大廈一單位，一名男住客報案，指早前隔鄰單位傳出陣陣異味，惡臭難頂，且愈來愈濃烈。警方接報到場調查，惟因臭味充斥走廊，到場調查警員均戴上口罩，而涉事單位無人應門，救援人員遂爆門入內，當打開門後湧出強烈的屍臭味，警員發現一具發黑腐爛，且有蛆虫的男性腐屍，躺臥近睡房位置地下。<br />\n<br />\n警員經初步調查，相信死者為獨居姓鄧(81歲)男戶主，估計已死去數星期，懷疑他跌倒後失救致死，並無可疑，屍體稍後由仵工舁送殮房，死因有待剖屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181001/bkn-20181001020642522-1001_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181001%2Fbkn-20181001020642522-1001_00822_001.html&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=394b8ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181001/bkn-20181001020642522-1001_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"161d898f42808c183f2f9e37349e30974cdc6277","tid":843164,"uid":182127,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔晚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5580077d11bc27099bcdd24c3e35e027d0aa4c","tid":843164,"uid":49974,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"已預知自己將來都會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\